song.title: Uuno Turhapuro Muuttaa Maalle - Ingame
song.info:
The game is based on the movie of the same name ("Uuno Turhapuro goes to countryside").
The Finnish low budget comedy movie (shot in 20 days) tells a story about notorious guy Uuno Turhapuro who this time moves to the countryside where his father produces illicit booze.
Recording is taken from Stone Oakvalley's site http://www.6581-8580.com/
